{"tid":778094,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"做咗5年高登砌機，你問我答（2）","createTime":"2018-08-13T12:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T12:47:36.000Z","uid":176405,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"62bf52f99c59e50f20745d88b2e3329a68dc7fee","tid":778094,"uid":176405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:02:27.000Z","msg":"我都無估到自己唔想再良心過意唔去嘅Post可以開到 (2)，多謝各位巴打支持，你地繼續問我繼續答啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個Post:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咗5年高登砌機，你問我答<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/768255/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/768255/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為腦細最近又壓人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔想做sales<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以應該最多過埋電腦節就唔撚做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寧願去做隻真&bull;IT狗都唔想再做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩都可以問，從行業秘密到砌機問題都可以問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見盡哂高登黃金砌機D仆街野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 砌機黃金定高登好？<br />\nA: 高登普遍好D，因為黃金鋪租貴過高登幾倍，所以正常都會貴D。同時都多釣水魚鋪，如Smart View、博毅。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 通常砌機會唔會被人Cap件、用二手野？<br />\nA: 大小鋪都會。睇你好唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ: Window、Office係咪淘寶野？<br />\nA: 好多，大鋪小鋪都會，有時會mix埋堅野買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ: 砌機散件好唔好搵？<br />\nA: 散件幾$ - 幾十$，砌機幾十$至五百。所以先會有咁多仆街野，否則圍唔至條數。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 邊間砌機好D ?<br />\nA: 睇個Sales，同你態度，通常愈格價一蚊都唔想被人賺，被人用二手件擴大利潤嘅機率通常會高D。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 砌機係咪大鋪好D？<br />\nA: 你去百佳買野會平過街市咩？仲有有時分分鐘正價俾套淘寶Window 你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ: 點預防被人玩？<br />\nA: 做好Research知自己要買咩就最實際。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再補充其他Q&amp;A集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c81bcbe2ca85ac645a2cfb4169506677b7ad7dc","tid":778094,"uid":31071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a165018f256ae2ae2c0539b4720efaf0a39d33a5","tid":778094,"uid":176405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c81bcbe2ca85ac645a2cfb4169506677b7ad7dc","tid":778094,"uid":31071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20e9b19688a0616af24fa6c71dc9eb2d69a6a49","tid":778094,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:10:30.000Z","msg":"邊D硬件牌子最伏/經常出事?"},{"pid":"74b33dd6cdee7d27d433f2346c90e00954b41c76","tid":778094,"uid":176405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e20e9b19688a0616af24fa6c71dc9eb2d69a6a49","tid":778094,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:10:30.000Z","msg":"邊D硬件牌子最伏/經常出事?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:18:46.000Z","msg":"睇Model具多<i